msgid ""
"Once you have your API keys, return to our platform's Automate section and "
"use them to link your OKX account with our automation system. This will "
"enable automated trading based on your TradingView alerts."
msgstr ""
"بمجرد حصولك على مفاتيح واجهة برمجة التطبيقات (API)، ارجع إلى قسم التشغيل "
