"Once you have your TradeLocker login credentials, return to our platform's "
"Automate section to link your TradeLocker account. This will enable "
"automated trading through our system based on your TradingView alerts."
msgstr ""
"بمجرد حصولك على بيانات اعتماد تسجيل الدخول إلى TradeLocker، ارجع إلى قسم "
